{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "ISB → Vendor Sync API",
    "description": "\nISB pushes **Staff**, **Family**, and **Department** master data to the vendor as\nsequential JSON batches. **ISB owns this request contract; the vendor implements\nan API that accepts exactly these request bodies.**\n\n### Endpoints\n- `POST /v1/sync/staffs` — one Staff batch `{\"staffs\": [...]}`\n- `POST /v1/sync/families` — one Family batch `{\"families\": [...]}`\n- `POST /v1/sync/departments` — one Department batch `{\"departments\": [...]}`\n\n### Authentication\nEach request carries the API key in the **`x-api-key`** HTTP header. *(Please confirm your endpoints accept `x-api-key`.)*\n\n### Batching\n- One batch per request, sent **sequentially** (no parallel calls).\n- Staff counts staff members; Family counts **family objects**; Department counts departments.\n- Current batch size: **up to 500 records per request** (please confirm acceptable + any rate limit).\n\n### Response contract *(to be finalised with vendor)*\n- Success: **HTTP 200** + `{\"status\":\"SUCCESS\",\"code\":\"200\",\"message\":\"Accepted\"}`.\n- Failure: `{\"status\":\"FAILED\",\"code\":\"...\",\"message\":\"...\"}`; bad/missing key → **401**, body not matching this schema → **422**.\n\n### Key field rules\n- `customerId` and `familyCode` are **integers** — never `202468.0`. `departmentId` is a **string**.\n- **Staff `login` is an object** `{loginId, email}`; **family parent `login` is a string** — intentional.\n- `secondaryParent` is `null` for single-parent families (the key is always present).\n- `smartCard.cardNumber` is `\"\"` when a person has no card; the `smartCard` object is **never omitted** (ISB decision).\n- **Department** carries **no `smartCard`** today (charged per department, not per card); a department `smartCard` may be added later (optional, **not sent currently** — please design to accept it without a breaking change). Optional `login` is an **object** like Staff.\n- Idempotency: re-sending the same `customerId` is an **upsert**; on conflict use **last-write-wins**.\n- `notificationEmails` may contain malformed addresses — accept them, do not reject.\n",
    "contact": {
      "name": "ISB Ed-Tech Center"
    },
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "paths": {
    "/v1/sync/staffs": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Sync"
        ],
        "summary": "Receive a Staff batch",
        "description": "POST one Staff batch `{\"staffs\": [...]}`. Staff `login` is an OBJECT.",
        "operationId": "sync_staffs_v1_sync_staffs_post",
        "parameters": [],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/StaffBatch"
              },
              "examples": {
                "staff_batch": {
                  "summary": "Staff batch (2 records)",
                  "description": "Note `login` is an object and `hasChildren` differs per record.",
                  "value": {
                    "staffs": [
                      {
                        "customerId": 202468,
                        "customerType": "Staff",
                        "staffType": "Classified Staff",
                        "department": "ED-TECH CENTER",
                        "familyCode": 202468,
                        "firstName": "Jirawat",
                        "lastName": "JIRACHAISOPIT",
                        "hasChildren": false,
                        "profileImage": "202468_SF.jpg",
                        "smartCard": {
                          "cardNumber": "D7F8F836"
                        },
                        "login": {
                          "loginId": "jirawatj@isb.ac.th",
                          "email": "jirawatj@isb.ac.th"
                        }
                      },
                      {
                        "customerId": 202301,
                        "customerType": "Staff",
                        "staffType": "Classified Staff",
                        "department": "MARKETING & COMMUNICATION",
                        "familyCode": 202301,
                        "firstName": "Somchai",
                        "lastName": "RAKDEE",
                        "hasChildren": true,
                        "profileImage": "202301_SF.jpg",
                        "smartCard": {
                          "cardNumber": "AA1100BB"
                        },
                        "login": {
                          "loginId": "somchair@isb.ac.th",
                          "email": "somchair@isb.ac.th"
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Accepted.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/SyncSuccess"
                },
                "example": {
                  "status": "SUCCESS",
                  "code": "200",
                  "message": "Accepted"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Missing / invalid API key.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "status": "FAILED",
                  "code": "401",
                  "message": "Invalid or missing API key (expected header 'x-api-key')."
                },
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "422": {
            "description": "Body does not match the contract.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "status": "FAILED",
                  "code": "422",
                  "message": "Request body does not match the ISB->Vendor contract.",
                  "errors": [
                    {
                      "type": "missing",
                      "loc": [
                        "body",
                        "staffs",
                        0,
                        "customerId"
                      ],
                      "msg": "Field required"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
